CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782866866
OL,3,CMothers of women killed by their
OL,4,Cpartners welcome sentencing changes
OL,6,FPoppy Devey Waterhouse, who was 24
OL,7,Fyears old, was murdered by her partner
OL,8,Fin 2018. He stabbed her repeatedly in
OL,9,Fthe head and cut her throat so that
OL,10,Fshe couldn't cry out. A hundred
OL,11,Finjuries. He got 16 years.
OL,13,FEllie Gould's killer got 12 and a half
OL,14,Fyears, because like her, he was 17. He
OL,15,Fleft the knife in her neck to try to
OL,16,Fclaim she'd killed herself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782866866
OL,3,CMothers of women killed by their
OL,4,Cpartners welcome sentencing changes
OL,6,FMegan Newborough's killer got 23 years
OL,7,F- a sentence extended because of so
OL,8,Fmany disturbing aggravating factors.
OL,9,FHe had almost decapitated her and
OL,10,Fdrove her body away from the house to
OL,11,Fdump it.
OL,13,FNow, after giving everything they had
OL,14,Fto campaign for change for seven long
OL,15,Fyears, their grieving mothers and
OL,16,Ftheir families believe they've
OL,17,Fachieved their aim of a change in
OL,18,Flegislation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
