PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782866866
OL,3,CMothers of women killed by their
OL,4,Cpartners welcome sentencing changes
OL,6,FThe Justice Secretary and Deputy PM
OL,7,FDavid Lammy has just announced plans
OL,8,Fto strengthen sentencing laws, which
OL,9,Fcould see those who kill a partner or
OL,10,Fex-partner at home with a knife or
OL,11,Fother weapon face an extra ten years
OL,12,Fin prison.
OL,14,FHe paid tribute to the mothers for
OL,15,Fwhat he called their courageous
OL,16,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782866866
OL,3,CMothers of women killed by their
OL,4,Cpartners welcome sentencing changes
OL,6,FThere are, however, some women's
OL,7,Fcampaigners who have deep reservations
OL,8,Fabout the change, about its possible
OL,9,Fimpact on abused women who kill their
OL,10,Fdomestic abusers.
OL,12,FEven though the government has said
OL,13,Ffor women in these circumstances, the
OL,14,Flower sentence would continue to
OL,15,Fapply, the Centre for Women's Justice
OL,16,Fis very concerned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782866866
OL,3,CMothers of women killed by their
OL,4,Cpartners welcome sentencing changes
OL,6,FThey say the government's plans have
OL,7,Fnot been fully thought through and
OL,8,Fpoint to a review of sentencing by
OL,9,FClare Wade KC in 2023, which reached
OL,10,Fvery different conclusions.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThey fear that an unintended
OL,18,Fconsequence for victims of domestic
OL,19,Fabuse who kill their abuser at home
OL,20,Fcould in fact see them face even
OL,21,Fharsher punishment as a result.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782866866
OL,3,CMothers of women killed by their
OL,4,Cpartners welcome sentencing changes
OL,6,FThe change to the law is now subject
OL,7,Fto consultation with the Sentencing
OL,8,FCouncil.
OL,10,FFor Elaine, Carole and Julie, the
OL,11,Frelief is profound - and the welcome
OL,12,Ffor the news immense.
OL,14,FStill speaking together, they said on
OL,15,FTuesday: "At last, women's lives are
OL,16,Fbeing valued as highly as men's....Our
OL,17,Fdaughters' lives were taken in brutal
OL,18,Fways as other women are killed every
OL,19,Fweek inside their home, the place they
OL,20,Fwere entitled to feel safe.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
