FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782866866
OL,3,CMothers of women killed by their
OL,4,Cpartners welcome sentencing changes
OL,6,F"The sentencing guidelines and
OL,7,Fstatutory schedules failed to properly
OL,8,Freflect this gross aggravating factor."
OL,10,FThey're now appealing for the change
OL,11,Fto come fast and for judges to
OL,12,Fimplement them soon.
OL,14,FIn the memory of all their daughters.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
